.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: grey, azure, amber, chestnut, white
Nationality: indonesian, mexican, polish, chinese, nigerian
Cigar: baccarat, whitemaster, havana, davidoff, pall-mall
Beverage: lemonade, almond-fanta, fanta, soy-milk, iced-tea
Pet: pony, ferret, hamster, lizard, goat

1. Nationality:indonesian == Color:grey
2. Nationality:mexican == Pet:pony
3. Beverage:lemonade == Color:azure
4. Nationality:polish == Beverage:almond-fanta
5. Color:azure is to the right of Color:amber
6. Cigar:baccarat == Pet:goat
7. Cigar:whitemaster == Color:chestnut
8. Beverage:fanta is in the middle
9. Nationality:chinese is on the far left
10. Cigar:havana is on the left or right of Pet:ferret
11. Cigar:whitemaster is to the left or right of Pet:lizard
12. Cigar:davidoff == Beverage:soy-milk
13. Nationality:nigerian == Cigar:pall-mall
14. Nationality:chinese is to the left or right of Color:white

.:: Answer ::.
